description: The registration of a custom AWS agent.

agentRegistrationId.description: The unique ID issued by Synapse when this agent was registered. Provide this ID when starting a session to use the registered agent for a session.

awsAgentId.description: The AWS issued agent ID of the agent.

awsAliasId.description: The AWS issued agent alias ID. If an alias ID was not provided, a default value of 'TSTALIASID' will be used.

registeredOn.description: The date this agent was registered.
